Bobertron entered earth's orbit. He smiled as the blue
shaped, primative, planet. It amazed him that the fate
of cybertron depended on who contoled the planet.
Bobertron was on cybertron when he got a call from his
old friend megs. He told him that his help was
needed.He was in fear of losing the war. Bobertron
left immediatly and now here he was. Soon he landed in
the ocean to get his beat mode. He found a sea
creature back to the dinosuar age skeleton inbede in a
rock. The name was unknown to him. It gave him great
strength and ability. He felt he could be great help
to his friend.
